        {
          "l": "খ",
          "m": 4,
          "q": "Show that \\(p^2+q^2 = 16\\). &nbsp; দেখাও যে \\(p^2+q^2=16\\)।",
          "sol": [
            {
              "t": "Use: \\(p^2+q^2 = (p+q)^2-2pq\\)"
            },
            {
              "m": "p+q = 2\\sqrt{5} \\implies (p+q)^2 = 20"
            },
            {
              "m": "p^2+q^2 = 20-2(2) = \\boxed{16}\\quad\\checkmark"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
